Value: Redstone Resources Limited explores for mineral properties in Australia. The company explores for copper and gold deposits. It holds 100% interest in the Tollu project located in the West Musgrave region of Western Australia. The company also holds 80% interest in the Hantails Gold project situated in the Kalgoorlie-Boulder, Western Australia. Redstone Resources Limited was incorporated in 1999 and is based in West Perth, Australia.
